"""
    Stop the template engine from rendering the contents of this block tag.

    Usage::

        {% verbatim %}
            {% don't process this %}
        {% endverbatim %}

    You can also designate a specific closing tag block (allowing the
    unrendered use of ``{% endverbatim %}``)::

        {% verbatim myblock %}
            ...
        {% endverbatim myblock %}
    """
